alaria and mobilising efforts to combat the disease.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-424_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-425_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-426_">Key facts and statistics</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/mohdizzuanbinroslan_9189aef4-9d35-452d-b1c1-4af36fbd37ab.jpg?v=1709570155" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/mohdizzuanbinroslan_9189aef4-9d35-452d-b1c1-4af36fbd37ab.jpg?v=1709570155 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/mohdizzuanbinroslan_9189aef4-9d35-452d-b1c1-4af36fbd37ab_1000x.jpg?v=1709570155 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/mohdizzuanbinroslan_9189aef4-9d35-452d-b1c1-4af36fbd37ab_500x.jpg?v=1709570155 320w" width="1000" height="667" alt="mohdizzuanbinroslan.jpeg__PID:48d14191-26c0-4303-b880-efd0e5a6bf55" title="Remembering Stonewall: Honouring the legacy of LGBTQ+ activism - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-428_"/><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-429_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by mohdizzuanbinroslan via Envato Elements</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-kYHfwS lkFAWj pf-431_"><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah cpQDEO pf-432_">According to the World Health Organisation (WHO), there were an estimated 241 million cases of malaria worldwide in 2020, with 627,000 deaths.</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah cpQDEO pf-434_">Malaria primarily affects vulnerable populations, including children under five years of age and pregnant women.</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah cpQDEO pf-436_">Sub-Saharan Africa remains the most affected region, accounting for approximately 94% of all malaria cases and deaths.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-438_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-439_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-440_">Raising awareness</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/caucasian-senior-mother-look-after-her-sick-daught-2023-11-27-05-28-24-utc.jpg?v=1709716327" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/caucasian-senior-mother-look-after-her-sick-daught-2023-11-27-05-28-24-utc.jpg?v=1709716327 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/caucasian-senior-mother-look-after-her-sick-daught-2023-11-27-05-28-24-utc_1000x.jpg?v=1709716327 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/caucasian-senior-mother-look-after-her-sick-daught-2023-11-27-05-28-24-utc_500x.jpg?v=1709716327 320w" width="1000" height="667" alt="Launching a Malaria Awareness Campaign: Tools and Tips for Success - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Launching a Malaria Awareness Campaign: Tools and Tips for Success - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-442_"/><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-443_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by s_kawee via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-445_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">World Malaria Day plays a crucial role in raising awareness about the impact of malaria on individuals, communities, and entire nations. Organisations such as the World Health Organisation (WHO), Malaria No More, and the Roll Back Malaria Partnership utilise this day to disseminate information, share key statistics, and educate the public about malaria prevention, symptoms, and treatment.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-447_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-448_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-449_">Mobilising action</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/close-up-or-macro-pictures-of-mosquitoes-on-the-sk-2023-11-27-05-14-14-utc.jpg?v=1709716398" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/close-up-or-macro-pictures-of-mosquitoes-on-the-sk-2023-11-27-05-14-14-utc.jpg?v=1709716398 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/close-up-or-macro-pictures-of-mosquitoes-on-the-sk-2023-11-27-05-14-14-utc_1000x.jpg?v=1709716398 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/close-up-or-macro-pictures-of-mosquitoes-on-the-sk-2023-11-27-05-14-14-utc_500x.jpg?v=1709716398 320w" width="1000" height="667" alt="The Global Fight Against Malaria: Progress and Challenges - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="The Global Fight Against Malaria: Progress and Challenges - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-451_"/><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-452_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by noteomg via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-454_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">The observance of World Malaria Day mobilises individuals, organisations, and governments to take action against malaria. Through advocacy campaigns, fundraising events, and community outreach programs, stakeholders worldwide unite in the fight against malaria. Organisations like the Global Fund to Fight AIDS, Tuberculosis, and Malaria provide crucial funding and resources to support malaria control efforts globally.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-456_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-457_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-458_">Engaging learners</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/learn-2023-11-27-05-13-23-utc.jpg?v=1709716464" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/learn-2023-11-27-05-13-23-utc.jpg?v=1709716464 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/learn-2023-11-27-05-13-23-utc_1000x.jpg?v=1709716464 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/learn-2023-11-27-05-13-23-utc_500x.jpg?v=1709716464 320w" width="1000" height="750" alt="Malaria Treatment and Control: Innovations and Best Practices - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Malaria Treatment and Control: Innovations and Best Practices - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-460_"/><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-461_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by wanaktek via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-463_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Educational institutions, NGOs, and online platforms leverage World Malaria Day to engage learners in meaningful ways. By incorporating discussions, workshops, and educational materials about malaria into curricula and training programs, learners gain a deeper understanding of the disease and the importance of collective action in combating it.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-465_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-x