Lah cpQDEO pf-477_">Support organisations such as Malaria No More, the Global Fund, and the British Red Cross in their efforts to combat malaria.</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah cpQDEO pf-479_">Advocate for increased funding and political commitment to malaria control and elimination efforts.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-481_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-482_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-483_">Uniting for a healthier future - The global fight against Malaria</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/africa-volunteering-charity-people-and-ecology-2023-11-27-05-32-45-utc.jpg?v=1709716640" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/africa-volunteering-charity-people-and-ecology-2023-11-27-05-32-45-utc.jpg?v=1709716640 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/africa-volunteering-charity-people-and-ecology-2023-11-27-05-32-45-utc_1000x.jpg?v=1709716640 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/africa-volunteering-charity-people-and-ecology-2023-11-27-05-32-45-utc_500x.jpg?v=1709716640 320w" width="1000" height="665" alt="Malaria No More: Initiatives That Are Making a Difference - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Malaria No More: Initiatives That Are Making a Difference - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-485_"/><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-486_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by ASphotostudio via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-488_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">World Malaria Day serves as a poignant reminder of the progress made in the fight against malaria and the challenges that remain. By coming together, raising awareness, and taking action, we can work towards a future where malaria no longer poses a threat to global health. Let us unite in our efforts to combat malaria and ensure a healthier, malaria-free world for generations to come.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-ca58" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-uojGG hMqLeX pf-490_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-ilfuhL bpQaoh"><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-491_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-492_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-493_">Related blog articles</h3><a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/pages/blogs" target="_blank" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Button2" class="sc-dtMgUX gJMWBM pf-495_">View all</a></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-497_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-498_"><img alt="{{ article_560875241541.image.alt }}" loading="eager" width="{{ article_560875241541.image.width }}" height="{{ article_560875241541.image.height }}" src="{% if article_560875241541.image %}
